&lt;p&gt;Due to an expansion in service, the Practice Development Team have vacancy for a new role of Clinical Education Facilitator. The post holder will work with the established team of Practice Facilitators and Educators supported by a Practice Development Lead. The role is clinically focussed, supporting learners in practice as well as management teams across the organisation and aims to support our staff to achieve our ambition of world class care in a positive practice environment. The role also involves clinical and classroom based teaching.&lt;/p&gt;
